text: Lycée Le Corbusier is a senior high school/sixth-form college in Aubervilliers, Seine-Saint-Denis, in the Paris metropolitan area. In 2014 83% of the students passed the baccalaureate, while in 2015 this increased to 90%. () ==References== ==External links== * Lycée Le Corbusier Category:Lycées in Seine-Saint-Denis
